# Experimental

Contains extended platform support that is community-confirmed but 
not yet hardware-tested by this repo's maintainer.

## me_cleaner_experimental.py

Adds on top of the stable fork:

- **ME 15 (Tiger Lake)** — HAP at `fpsba+0x7C` PCHSTRP31, community confirmed
- **ME 16 / 16.1 (Alder Lake / Raptor Lake)** — HAP in Flash Descriptor 
  offset `0x017E`, community confirmed. Previous guess of `fpsba+0xDC` was wrong.
- **ME 18 (Meteor Lake)** — same as ADL/RPL, descriptor `0x017E`

Use at your own risk. If you test this and it works, please open an issue 
and report your platform and ME version so it can be promoted to stable.
